## üéØ Core Principle

**Avoid distributional convergence.** Generic design choices (Inter fonts, purple gradients, minimal animations) dominate training data. Without direction, AI models default to safe, universal choices that undermine brand identity and make AI-generated interfaces immediately recognizable‚Äîand dismissible.

**Solution:** Provide targeted, domain-specific guidance that steers away from generic defaults toward distinctive, brand-aligned design.

